sentence: where can i eat french food in mountain view ?
sentence-with-vars: where can i eat VARfood food in VARcity ?
sql: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from LOCATION,RESTAURANT where LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID and LOCATION.CITY_NAME='mountain view' and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='french'
sql-with-vars: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from LOCATION,RESTAURANT where LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID and LOCATION.CITY_NAME='VARcity' and RESTAURANT.FOOD_TYPE='VARfood'
